553
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:38,120
Was Mrs. Qin's death related to the surgery?

554
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:40,440
No. The surgery was successful.

555
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,640
Now Qin Gang believes

556
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:45,400
that Mrs. Qin's death was related to the surgery.

557
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:46,400
Did you know that?

558
00:31:49,120 --> 00:31:49,680
I did.

559
00:31:50,800 --> 00:31:52,330
Do you know why I'm leaving?

560
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:54,840
Because staying here

561
00:31:56,760 --> 00:31:58,090
has no meaning anymore.

562
00:31:58,840 --> 00:32:00,840
Don't you want to explain yourself?

563
00:32:02,080 --> 00:32:03,410
I don't want to explain.

564
00:32:06,520 --> 00:32:08,360
But now everyone believes

565
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:11,480
that Mrs. Qin died because of a failed surgery.

566
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:13,820
It doesn't matter.

567
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:16,160
Being a doctor is a matter of conscience.

568
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:18,280
I have a clear conscience, that's enough.

569
00:32:18,280 --> 00:32:20,760
You know better than I do

570
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:22,720
how important reputation is for a doctor.

571
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:24,980
You finally picked up the scalpel again,

572
00:32:26,320 --> 00:32:27,980
and now you're just giving up?

573
00:32:28,520 --> 00:32:29,250
I don't care.

574
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:30,360
I do.

575
00:32:37,120 --> 00:32:37,800
Thank you.

576
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:41,100
At a time like this,

577
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:44,480
you still care about my reputation. Thank you.

578
00:32:45,040 --> 00:32:46,170
You misunderstood.

579
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:49,900
I was the one who begged you to do the surgery.

580
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:52,920
If something went wrong, I'm responsible.

581
00:32:55,080 --> 00:32:56,640
I came here today to tell you

582
00:32:58,000 --> 00:33:00,040
you can leave, go anywhere you want.

583
00:33:00,360 --> 00:33:01,490
No one will stop you.

584
00:33:02,240 --> 00:33:03,520
But before you go,

585
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:06,290
you must explain this situation clearly.

586
00:33:08,320 --> 00:33:10,520
Otherwise, I won't let you off the hook.

587
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:12,840
Xinxin.

588
00:33:18,240 --> 00:33:19,240
How is Bao doing?

589
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:21,370
I'm not as mature as you are,

590
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:25,700
I don't think things through as thoroughly.

591
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:28,410
But when I set my mind on something,

592
00:33:29,680 --> 00:33:31,540
I will definitely see it through.

593
00:33:32,160 --> 00:33:35,520
When I face difficulties,

594
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:37,640
I accept them,

595
00:33:39,280 --> 00:33:40,340
and overcome them.

596
00:33:44,080 --> 00:33:46,520
That's what someone I once loved taught me.

597
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:53,520
Of course, this is your business.

598
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:57,160
Make your own decision.

599
00:34:08,639 --> 00:34:11,040
You should go upstairs and get some sleep now.

600
00:34:11,040 --> 00:34:12,719
I'll keep track of the time for you.

601
00:34:12,719 --> 00:34:15,120
I'll get you some late-night snacks later.

602
00:34:15,520 --> 00:34:17,960
Your favorite seafood porridge. Okay?

603
00:34:21,120 --> 00:34:22,000
You know what?

604
00:34:23,600 --> 00:34:25,239
You're now the only person

605
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:27,560
in this world who cares about me.

606
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:29,639
Alright.

607
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:32,130
If you behave, I'll care for you even more.

608
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:33,360
Good boy.

609
00:34:34,000 --> 00:34:34,960
Okay, go now.

610
00:35:06,040 --> 00:35:07,770
Did you two plan this together?

611
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:09,080
Plan what?

612
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:10,200
Is there anything else?

613
00:35:10,200 --> 00:35:11,400
I'm starving. Give me

614
00:35:12,120 --> 00:35:13,050
one serving too.

615
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:16,700
This is the only pack left.

616
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:22,080
What is this? It's not properly soaked.

617
00:35:22,080 --> 00:35:23,920
You eat this alone at home?

618
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:26,660
Does it look like I have any stock at home?

619
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:28,960
Fine, I'll take this.

620
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:34,160
When are you leaving?

621
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:36,010
I'm not leaving.

622
00:35:37,240 --> 00:35:38,370
You're not leaving?

623
00:35:39,160 --> 00:35:41,090
But didn't you already make plans?

624
00:35:42,560 --> 00:35:43,520
Xinxin came by.

625
00:35:45,160 --> 00:35:46,200
I thought so.

626
00:35:46,480 --> 00:35:47,940
She convinced you to stay?

627
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:51,660
She asked me to explain everything clearly before I leave.

628
00:35:54,120 --> 00:35:55,120
That's good news.

629
00:35:55,240 --> 00:35:56,760
I think she's testing you.

630
00:35:57,480 --> 00:36:00,080
Look, her attitude toward you

631
00:36:00,080 --> 00:36:01,560
has softened a lot lately.

632
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,260
I really hope that's true.

633
00:36:05,560 --> 00:36:08,090
I'm afraid I might be reading too much into it.

634
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:11,520
Why don't I ask her for you?

635
00:36:11,520 --> 00:36:12,480
No, no, no.

636
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:15,200
I can speak for myself.

637
00:36:15,200 --> 00:36:17,600
Don't help. You'll just make things worse.

638
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:20,120
You've changed a lot.

639
00:36:21,520 --> 00:36:22,760
You wouldn't say a word before.

640
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:24,120
Now you're so proactive.

641
00:36:24,120 --> 00:36:25,450
Well, I have to improve.

642
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:27,580
Although I'm much older than you,

643
00:36:27,720 --> 00:36:28,680
I think you young people

644
00:36:28,680 --> 00:36:30,920
have really good approaches sometimes.

645
00:36:30,920 --> 00:36:32,400
Especially you and Wan Xinxin.

646
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:33,760
Sometimes to accomplish something,

647
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:35,290
you're both so determined.

648
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,920
That's how love should be.

649
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:38,440
Of course, you're different.

650
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:41,300
You're all over the place. Completely unreliable.

651
00:36:43,680 --> 00:36:45,280
Why do I feel like you're insulting me?

652
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:46,080
But I'm glad.

653
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:47,520
And then?

654
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:51,880
Then there's hope.

655
00:36:52,440 --> 00:36:53,640
I have to try.

656
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:55,000
And then?

657
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:58,120
Then since there's hope and I need to try,

658
00:36:58,120 --> 00:37:00,040
I have to work harder.

659
00:37:01,240 --> 00:37:01,770
And then?

660
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:07,370
Then I think it's really strange that you came today.

661
00:37:08,160 --> 00:37:08,880
And then?

662
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:13,680
Then I think you just came here for a free meal.

663
00:37:13,680 --> 00:37:15,010
That's right. And then?

664
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:17,860
Then if you don't leave, I'm going to hit you.

665
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:26,680
Who wants to eat this terrible noodles? They're not even properly soaked.

666
00:37:26,680 --> 00:37:27,210
And then?

667
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:29,730
Let's go.

668
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:30,520
Xu Ke.

669
00:37:32,480 --> 00:37:34,540
Having you as a friend makes me happy.

670
00:37:36,080 --> 00:37:36,610
And then?

671
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:39,600
Gosh, really.

672
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:40,970
Let's go.

673
00:37:44,200 --> 00:37:44,730
Hua Ming.

674
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:47,520
Good luck!

675
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:55,200
Kaiyang, quick!

676
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:58,240
Tell me what's going on right now.

677
00:37:58,240 --> 00:38:00,040
Worst case, we'll turn ourselves in.

678
00:38:00,040 --> 00:38:00,560
Well...

679
00:38:01,520 --> 00:38:02,160
I know.

680
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:05,080
But I'm hungry. Can we make dinner first?

681
00:38:05,080 --> 00:38:06,940
After cooking, while I'm eating,

682
00:38:07,720 --> 00:38:08,800
I'll tell you everything.

683
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:09,960
Fine. During dinner,

684
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:13,020
you'll tell me everything that's been weighing on you.

685
00:38:34,080 --> 00:38:34,610
Kaiyang.

686
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:37,810
Kaiyang, open the door.

687
00:38:38,080 --> 00:38:39,640
I'll be back first thing tomorrow morning.

688
00:38:39,640 --> 00:38:40,800
Open the door.

689
00:38:41,120 --> 00:38:42,160
Open up, Kaiyang.

690
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:43,920
Open the door.

691
00:38:45,080 --> 00:38:47,880
Kaiyang, don't do anything foolish.

692
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:55,260
Please don't do anything stupid.

693
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,800
I can pick it up with chopsticks.

694
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:34,640
Try it.

695
00:40:36,200 --> 00:40:36,730
How is it?

696
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:38,600
It's good.

697
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:41,780
It fits well. The shoulders are perfect too.

698
00:40:41,920 --> 00:40:43,400
It's good.

699
00:41:40,120 --> 00:41:41,850
You don't need to look anymore.

700
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:43,890
Starting tomorrow,

701
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:46,730
all the company assets will belong to you.

702
00:41:50,240 --> 00:41:51,040
They're ours.

703
00:41:53,080 --> 00:41:55,410
What are your plans when you get the money?

704
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:58,680
You don't need to ask about that.

705
00:41:58,680 --> 00:41:59,680
I just want to know

706
00:42:00,120 --> 00:42:01,640
when I can get my money.

707
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:06,460
You have to give me some time to sell the company,

708
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:08,660
and I need to find the right buyer.

709
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:10,460
Here's what you do.

710
00:42:11,320 --> 00:42:13,320
First transfer the money to the company account,

711
00:42:13,320 --> 00:42:15,320
because it's a significant amount.

712
00:42:21,720 --> 00:42:23,180
I hope by tomorrow morning

713
00:42:23,200 --> 00:42:26,400
you'll deposit at least half the money into this account.

714
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:28,560
You're being too impatient.

715
00:42:29,120 --> 00:42:30,450
Didn't we agree on this?

716
00:42:33,240 --> 00:42:36,170
Qin Gang's company is investing in a new project now,

717
00:42:36,640 --> 00:42:38,300
even if all the money is spent.

718
00:43:44,440 --> 00:43:44,840
Li.

719
00:43:46,480 --> 00:43:46,800
Li.

720
00:43:48,520 --> 00:43:49,180
Li Wengang.

721
00:43:49,240 --> 00:43:49,760
Jiang Qiaohua.

